      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLUE LAKODA (2) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at Q Straight (16.56) last time and making it two straight wins. Solid record here winning two races. Has the ability and expected to prove tough to beat again. NEW YORK LIBERTY (3) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from five starts. Comes off a (19.53) win last time, scoring by 2.75 lengths in a Grade 6 over 352m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. JALAPENO POPPER (1) was out of in the placings when sixth last time but prior to that posted a slick 23.81 win over 407m at Rockhampton. Must include on winning run two back. HELLO ELSA (7) is in fine form and looks a good top-three chance again.",
